SplashBox Natural Language Framework

Use the following steps to run the service:
 - Download aiml files:
   - cd service/aiml && ./download-aiml.sh
 - Run chat server. (The chatbot brain)
   - ./service/chat-service &

Available Bots Now:
 - A chat bot: action/chat
 - A command bot: action/command

The Level-0 natural language parser: (not fully ready)
 - Action parser
   - ./scripts/parser-0.pl run firefox --> /tmp/splashbox/now/UUID.xml will be created.

 - Chat messages (Not implemented)
   - All other messages will be all sent to action/chat as a chat messages.



